1.6.0 [2026-06-16]
  ⚠️ Version 1.5 is the last version for DSM 6.x
  
  IMPLEMENTATIONS:
 - [GUI]    🔥 A graphical folder picker has been implemented so that folder paths can be selected directly.
            Target folders can be created automatically in the folder picker.
 - [GUI]    "title" can now be set in metadata (GUI ➜ OCR options: --title my title).
            All rename parameters can also be set as variables.
 - [GUI]    Option to manually restore the configuration database.
 - [GUI]    NameSyntax editor improved: placeholders can now be conveniently inserted as chips via drag & drop.
 - [GUI]    The overview page now features a real-time progress indicator.
 - [GUI]    Package server for convenient updates can now be added automatically to Package Center via a button.
 - [shell]  Backup files are now tracked in the database.
            This ensures clean rotation even for older files or when the scanner's system time is incorrect. (issue #79)
            In the GUI, the user can define how to handle orphaned entries.
            ⚠️ Existing backup files will fall out of rotation with this update and may need to be deleted manually.
 
  IMPROVEMENT:
 - [GUI]    Hints and instructions for setting up the package server if it has not already been configured in DSM.
 - [GUI]    Immediate display of path validation.
 - [GUI]    Warning about unsaved changes.
 - [shell]  OCR-optimized black and white conversion.
 - [shell]  Delay optimization for the case when the scanner clock is ahead (#82 thanks to @tacarrie).
 - [shell]  Revision of logging, log file layouts and error logging.
 - [shell]  Revision / hardening of database access.
 - [pkg]    preinst/preupgrade: Early check for Python ≥ 3.9 on aarch64.

  BUGFIXES:
 - [shell]  Compatibility with aarch64 restored.
 - [shell]  Minor bug fixes.
 - [YAML]   Tag names containing the character „&" led to incorrect naming.
